{"tid":1866284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"病房變殮房 武漢如「屍變城市」","createTime":"2020-02-06T16:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T16:27:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd7241fe862e9ff33d5bacfd6d47eefa13d306c","tid":1866284,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200206/CA6ZRHZ7CVNQKR4R3PNOSM2AUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200206%2FCA6ZRHZ7CVNQKR4R3PNOSM2AUQ%2F&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=c09c52b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200206%2FCA6ZRHZ7CVNQKR4R3PNOSM2AUQ%2F&h=a0ffca31\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200206/CA6ZRHZ7CVNQKR4R3PNOSM2AUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n病房變殮房 武漢如「屍變城市」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地疫情失控，確診武漢肺炎的案例直逼2.5萬宗，多地「封城」防疫。內地近日瘋傳武漢住院患者與屍體共處一室的影片，武漢網民指當地早已變成「屍變城市」。有指影片拍於半個月前，未能反映眼前實況。至於13間「方艙醫院」由於無防護、無隔離，網民批評是等死的集中營。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台在Twitter上指出，武漢網民周二（4日）曝光一段醫院現場影片，顯示無論病房還是候診室，都變成臨時殮房，一些病人被迫在沒有防護隔離的狀態下，與屍體同處一室；另有其他影片顯示，一長排的屍體放在走廊，情況十分嚇人。內地網民對此議論紛紛。有人指前者是攝於半個月前，「搶救室和停屍間放屍體不是很正常，不要惡意誇大事實」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200206/large/1580919311_a461.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200206%2Flarge%2F1580919311_a461.gif&h=8c716038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網傳武漢醫院病人與屍體共處一室。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倉卒建院像「等死集中營」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：三方施壓奏效 林鄭終跪低<br />\n<br />\n武漢政府為控制疫情，除速建火神山醫院，近日又連夜將體育館、展覽中心等改造成13間「方艙醫院」。這些醫院的內部完全無防護、無隔離，病床放得密密麻麻。網民批評，只會造成傳染情況更為嚴重，批評「這根本是等死的集中營」。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台"},{"pid":"006f8f5f9d029f62910e9b95dae984fd9cc48f90","tid":1866284,"uid":84102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:12:38.000Z","msg":"無事兒 無事兒 只是普通袋子而已 別胡亂散播謠言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63020350760d0268acbf0991d2d392f17f1426e3","tid":1866284,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3da401b540058b84f3c5b1f929064b7ffe9029f0","tid":1866284,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c0c6358dd24702333fd7585f3e76ae8c3534ad","tid":1866284,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"如果認真集齊網上有嘅武漢片同相，逐條屍數分分鐘仲多過個官方數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff750c095c58505adf5159efd6cdf3c924e567f","tid":1866284,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce122b3e502323923ed6df72baf2c2c88d61ad49","tid":1866284,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"難以想像相中人有幾大陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17df480bdff125854d83edaf151e141dfbbb265c","tid":1866284,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:23:28.000Z","msg":"可以等投胎下世唔做支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52c7f26a90495f8dd2feb24a3380b1104ba2c7e","tid":1866284,"uid":93277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"大陸無殮房架咩?"},{"pid":"b7e92b40ba16ed268da387e2ce9c79123b3f91a0","tid":1866284,"uid":273635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"支那表示: 反正你遲早都死  病房同殮房都係一樣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cfa89e3b9